ygData.messageBody:
I can totally sympathize with that. Having just gained lvl 9 Friday, I put
in about 10 hours worth of time over Saturday and Sunday trying to get some
buffer so I wouldn't lose it. I picked the WRONG weekend.. hehe. After 10
hours of play and 3 deaths, I have yet to fill the first quarter of the
first bubble. The funny thing is though, that I haven't been knocked down to
8th! Talk about walkin a fine line...
